php-nlgen (0.18)

	* Availability fixes plus web demo.

-- Pablo Duboue, 2022/10/11

php-nlgen (0.17)

	* A full grammar for generating availability descriptions based on schedules.
	* Lexicon: added query_string to streamline calls.
	* Generator: compilation with namespaces and wired-in lexicons and ontology.
	* Basic test cases.

-- Pablo Duboue, 2022/10/05

php-nlgen (0.16)

	* Lexicon query improvements and error notifications.

-- Pablo Duboue, 2022/08/30

php-nlgen (0.15)

	* Lexicon now takes slotted strings.

-- Pablo Duboue, 2022/08/24

php-nlgen (0.14)

	* Method interception now does not pollute the semantic stack with
	'_orig' or the language used.
	* Added new static 'Compile' method to use in servers with no 'eval' enabled.
	* Improved basic examples.

-- Pablo Duboue, 2022/08/24

php-nlgen (0.13)

	* Method interception now works with multilingual extensions.

-- Pablo Duboue, 2022/08/22

php-nlgen (0.12)

	* Published the SimpleTechnicalEnglish as a grammar part of the
	library instead of an example.

-- Pablo Duboue, 2020/09/06

php-nlgen (0.11)

	* Uppercase names for packagist release
	* composer.json

-- Pablo Duboue, 2020/09/06

